{"word":"Bath-Sheba","slug":"bath-sheba","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bath-Sheba</b> <a href=\"#/H1339\">H1339</a> <br/> Wife of Uriah and later wife of David.<br/> Called Bathshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=5'>1Ch 3:5</a><br/> Adultery of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=5'>2Sa 11:5</a><br/> Solomon's mother<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=31'>1Ki 1:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=21'>1Ki 2:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=5'>1Ch 3:5</a>"}]}